@VanLife.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7250
@SellerId = 2cb91a52-42b5-4f59-9f3a-a96925f90488
@UserId = {{SellerId}}
@VanId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@ImageId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Vans (shared filters + pagination + skip)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vans?page=1&pageSize=5&skip=0&category=Luxury&minPrice=50&maxPrice=300
Accept: application/json

### Van details (copy VanId from list)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vans/{{VanId}}
Accept: application/json

### Van management details
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vans/{{VanId}}/management
Accept: application/json

### Rent van
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vans/{{VanId}}/rent?days=3
Accept: application/json

###
### Auth - sign up
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Daisy",
  "lastName": "Sophia",
  "email": "daisy@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123!",
  "role": "Buyer"
}

### Auth - single reusable login endpoint
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "buyer@vanlife.com",
  "password": "Buyer123!",
  "role": "Buyer"
}

### Auth - forgot password
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "buyer@vanlife.com"
}

### Auth - reset password
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "buyer@vanlife.com",
  "newPassword": "NewBuyer123!",
  "confirmPassword": "NewBuyer123!"
}

###
### Dashboard - seller summary (vans + transactions)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/sellers/{{SellerId}}?page=1&pageSize=5&skip=0&days=30
Accept: application/json

### Dashboard - income graph
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/income-graph?year=2026&sellerId={{SellerId}}
Accept: application/json

### Dashboard - transactions (shared filters + pagination + skip)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/transactions?page=1&pageSize=5&skip=0&days=14&minPrice=100
Accept: application/json

###
### Reviews (shared filters + pagination + skip)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/reviews?userId={{UserId}}&page=1&pageSize=5&skip=0&startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31&reviewType=Positive
Accept: application/json

###
### Images
### Upload
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/images/upload?fileName=van-photo.jpg&vanId={{VanId}}
Accept: application/json

### List images (pagination + skip)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/images?page=1&pageSize=10&skip=0
Accept: application/json

### Delete image (copy ImageId from list)
DELETE {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/images/{{ImageId}}
Accept: application/json

###
### 404 test
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/this-does-not-exist
Accept: application/json
